            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "BRST"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " In the case of experimental Setup 1 - the",
                "bremsstrahlung gamma radiation was generated by",
                "passing a pulsed electron beam at end-point energy",
                "range 35...95 MeV through a tantalum metal plate, 1.05",
                "1.05 mm in thickness. The Ta-converter was fixed on the",
                "aluminum cylinder, 100 mm in diameter and 150 mm in",
                "thickness.",
                "For Setup 2 - the bremsstrahlung radiation was",
                "generated by passing an electron beam at end-point",
                "energies Egmax = 42.4; 60.4, and 80.5 MeV through the",
                "Ta foil, 0.1 mm in thickness and without Al-absorber."
              ]
            }
          ],
